        <para>
            <emph type="bold">Refrigerant Oil (By Type)</emph>All R-12*, and HFC-134A** air conditioning systems use 12
            oz. of refrigerant oil. If the system is being replaced with all new components, or after a system flush,
            add an additional 4 oz. of refrigerant.
        </para>
        <para>*Use only mineral based refrigerant oil in R-12 systems.</para>
        <para>**Use only Lubrizol LZ2916 Ester oil in HFC-134A systems.</para>
